  "_comment_architecture": [
    "Pattern A: PEF/Carbon footprint OBSERVATION.",
    "",
    "An LCA practitioner re-runs the PEFCR Apparel & Footwear methodology against",
    "this individual jacket using lot-specific supplier data, and records the",
    "result against the inspection event. The score IS the observation, so",
    "environmentalFootprint stays at EVENT level; it captures what was",
    "measured at this point in time, not the product's published declaration.",
    "",
    "Use this pattern when: the score may differ across lots / inspections, or",
    "the event itself is what produced the value.",
    "Use the declaration pattern (declaration-environmental-footprint.jsonld)",
    "when: the score is the product's authoritative published PEF declaration",
    "that travels with every unit of this SKU.",
    "",
    "HTTP header: GS1-Extensions: oec=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/common/core/,eutex=https://ref.openepcis.io/extensions/eu/textile/",
    "See: core/docs/EPCIS_MASTERDATA_AND_EXTENSIONS.md",
    "GS1 demo prefix 952 (7-digit GCP: 9521234)."
  ],
